/*
 * TODO:
 * - Axis roles enforce classes; Have DEFENDER Covi stay on scaffolding goals, and DEFENDER1 Engi close to Main Gate Power? With specific raised priorities
 *		* Perhaps if Axis get to ground level by sides and not front, it'd safer for them? (3)
 * - main_gate_power_Planted: Axis Smokebomb mid-way walls/power box?
 * - MOBILEMORTAR_Walls: DEFEND_MainGate is within radius... Tempted to let it be
 * - Start - Axis: jumping into water does not seem the brightest idea... or get out faster/safer (3)
 * - Main Entrance Power cover spot: bot runs towards the dyna, change it to 30 sec
 *
 * - Do Axis defend the room flag? A single DEFEND_AxisFlag... and DEFEND_MansionFront (6 spots) covering Mansion front _only_
 *		* DEFEND_Mansion inside but not focused on room flag
 *		* ATTACK_Charlie1/2/3 are the Allies equivalent (4 covers the back of the Mansion...) - Change them to CAMP_RoomFlag or something
 * - Cover/Detonate spots
 * - Move PLANT_Basement_Bridge position at the other side
 * - K43 results too much in selfkill... only when the focus is inside the walls
 * - Axis tripmines?
 * - DEFEND_WaterwayDoorDestroyed management is a mess
 * - Try to see if it's possible to exclude tomb stones from being targeted
 *		* Once in 2nd phase, change the TargetBreakableDist to 0 (have a Map var for late joiners)
 * - PLANT_Crypt_Gate > PLANT_Axis_Command_Post for Covis
 * - PLANTMINE_Obj should be off when Crypt Gate gets built and Catacomb Door isn't destroyed
 * - I tried to make Axis jump in the Crypt area near a tree south, seems to fail hard...
 * - Make use of the Axis Soldier during this phase while Allies own the flag
 * - Due to role, DEFENDER rarely has Engi to do PLANTMINE_Garden
 *
 * - If Crypt Gate gets built after obj taken and Catacomb Door is intact, have the bot suicide if stuck inside
 *		* Or cover the Catacomb Door from that side...
 * - When stealing the Book, goals are roughly managed; disable Engi goals at least... excepted PLANT_Crypt_Gate! (2)
 *		* Also Soldier (MG at Main Gate?) + Arty on Raft
 * - Obj taken: split Allies spawn?
 * - Obj taken: too much focus on room flag and not Raft area...
 *
 * - Book_of_the_Resurrection_Secured: Axis suicide spawn if not on Walls
 * - Mortar on Raft when it's not escorted back by Axis?
 */

// DEFEND_start3/4/6 => DEFEND_Walls1/2/3
// DEFEND_start1/2/5/7 => DEFEND_WallsGround1/2/3/4
// DEFEND_Alpha => DEFEND_MansionFront
// DEFEND_Bravo => DEFEND_Mansion & DEFEND_Backyard
// DEFEND_Delta => DEFEND_Book
// DEFEND_End

// DEFEND_AxisFlag
